The Centre Léon Bérard is dedicated 100% to cancer care and research

     * Care
     * Research
     * Training
     * International vision

EXCELLENCE & INNOVATION in cancer care and research

   A non-profit private healthcare facility, the Centre Léon Bérard is
   affiliated to the National Federation of Centers for the Fight Against
   Cancer – Unicancer – which comprises 20 centers in France.
     __________________________________________________________________

Our missions in a few words

Care

   The Centre Léon Bérard is a hospital that is dedicated 100% to cancer
   care and research. Its intention is to offer excellent care and to be a
   referral center for people with cancer.
   Cancer center

Research

   The Center’s main objective is to develop excellent and
   multidisciplinary research in collaboration with the healthcare
   activity of the Centre Léon Bérard, together with institutional and
   private partners.
   Research

Teaching

   Teaching and training are currently a strength of the Centre Léon
   Bérard.
   Transferring excellence in cancerology
